  "body": "At present, the Gas price on the ETH network is very expensive. Even so, I found that some transactions still achieve 0 Gas Price. I want to know, how should I do it and realize it?\r\n\r\nExample: https://etherscan.io/tx/0x2d10ea087d1f8a70f31e504356d45face7f086af5fabab0ef1bc24400f532c5f\r\n\r\nI built the Geth node myself and used it for an ETH miner. I can send the transaction to my Geth node and mine at the same time. But it seems that my transaction will not be packaged.",
